# 📚 Library Book Tracker (MySQL Project)

A simple but well-structured **Library Management System** built using MySQL.  
This project demonstrates relational database design, SQL queries, and real-world data modeling.

---

## 🧩 Project Overview

This system manages:
- 👤 Library Members
- 📚 Books Collection
- 📖 Borrowing Records

It tracks which member borrows which book, including borrow dates, due dates, and return status.

