## 🗂️ Database Structure

### 👤 Members Table
Stores library users and their information.

### 📚 Books Table
Stores all available books in the library.

### 📖 Borrowing Table
Links members and books and tracks borrowing activity.

---

## 🔗 Relationships

- One Member → Many Borrowings  
- One Book → Many Borrowings  
- Borrowing table acts as a bridge (many-to-many relationship)

---

